nal hygiene reasons or to have some steady WiFi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8.jpg\" alt=\"camping in costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"267\" height=\"338\" alt=\"camping in costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-78865 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1515px) 100vw, 1515px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8.jpg 1515w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-473x600.jpg 473w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-639x810.jpg 639w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-267x338.jpg 267w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-129x163.jpg 129w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-142x180.jpg 142w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-606x768.jpg 606w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-808x1024.jpg 808w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-852x1080.jpg 852w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-1136x1440.jpg 1136w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-300x380.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-600x760.jpg 600w, 