e campsites, and the infrastructure is fine but should not be compared to popular camping countries like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">France<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>See here <a href=\"#itinerary\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">our complete camping itinerary with (wild) campsites<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/77089&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24110929\/camping-costa-rica-itinerary-4.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24110929\/camping-costa-rica-itinerary-4-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24110929\/camping-costa-rica-itinerary-4-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Camping in Costa Rica with a 4&#xD7;4: The Ultimate Road Trip Itinerary\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-is-camping-in-costa-safe\">Is camping in Costa safe?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You might be wondering, &#x2018;Is Costa Rica even safe for camping?&#x2019;. Yes, Costa Rica is generally considered a very <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-safety\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">safe travel<\/a> destination. However, that doesn&#x2019;t mean you should leave all your doors open and items in eyesight. Like in most parts of the world, there&#x2019;s always one person that might take the opportunity to steal. However, if you apply the basic rules and follow your gut instinct, you will have the time of your life!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Here are our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-safety\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">tips for traveling safe<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/23105355\/camping-costa-rica-29.jpg\