ank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/23105355\/camping-costa-rica-29.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Camping in campsites will most likely increase your safety compared to wild camping, but from our experience and stories from other travelers we met, both options are safe.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>The <a href=\"https:\/\/translate.google.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Google Translate<\/a> app is extremely helpful if your Spanish isn&#x2019;t that good. It has a camera option that translates full sentences in seconds.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-but-what-about-dangerous-animals\">But what about dangerous animals?<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>You will encounter many animals in Costa Rica. Luckily, most of them are not dangerous. Whenever you enter and leave your tent or cabin, check the surroundings and avoid stepping into any overgrown grass and bushes.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Within our 3 weeks of camping, we didn&#x2019;t come into contact with any dangerous animals. We did see snakes and spiders, but that&#x2019;s when we went searching for them, specifically in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Manual Antonio National Park<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/tortuguero\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tortuguero<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12172612\/Tortuguero-7.jpg\" alt=\"spiders costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"spiders costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-75646 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12172612\/Tortuguero-7.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12172612\/Tortuguero-7-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12172612\/Tortuguero-7-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12172612\/Tortuguero-7-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12172612\/Tortuguero-7-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12172612\/Tortuguero-7-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12172612\/Tortuguero-7-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12172612\/Tortuguero-7-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12172612\/Tortuguero-7-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12172612\/Tortuguero-7-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12172612\/Tortuguero-7-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/upload