ng experience much easier.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-camping-and-campsite-facilities\">Camping and campsite facilities&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember that you will not have a toilet when wild camping. All campsites have cold showers, which can be a challenge, especially in the highlands, where it&#x2019;s cooler outside.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144004\/camping-costa-rica-17.jpg\" alt=\"campsite showers costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"campsite showers costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-78883 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144004\/camping-costa-rica-17.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144004\/camping-costa-rica-17-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144004\/camping-costa-rica-17-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144004\/camping-costa-rica-17-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144004\/camping-costa-rica-17-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144004\/camping-costa-rica-17-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144004\/camping-costa-rica-17-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144004\/camping-costa-rica-17-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144004\/camping-costa-rica-17-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144004\/camping-costa-rica-17-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploa