            <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>In Costa Rica, water is free and drinkable in most parts of the country. We bought a 10 liter water bottle at the supermarket once and refilled this entire road trip!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-1080x721.jpg\" alt=\"reusable water bottle\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"reusable water bottle\" class=\"wp-image-47339 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.