 dripper, and sometimes even a hammock and shower! Additionally, a phone with a connection can be provided as a WiFi hotspot.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1.jpg\" alt=\"camping in costa rica nomad america\"><\/noscript><img width=\"429\" height=\"338\" alt=\"camping in costa rica nomad america\" class=\"wp-image-79031 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-762x600.jpg 762w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-1029x810.jpg 1029w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-429x338.jpg 429w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-30x24.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-163x128.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-229x180.jpg 229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-768x604.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-1024x806.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-1372x1080.jpg 1372w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-1830x1440.jpg 1830w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-300x236.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-600x472.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-150x118.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1-30x24.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/24111505\/camping-costa-rica-28-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can reach Nomad America 24\/7 through a Whatsapp group with all your questions during your camping road trip. You are only allowed to drive cars if you&#x2019;re 18 or older.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The small cars are suitable for two people, but if you&#x2019;re with more than opt for a larger car. Prices range from 80 USD to 196 USD per day.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-4x4-truck-camper-from-nomad-america\">4&#xD7;4 Truck Camper from Nomad America<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We rented the Kia 4&#xD7;4 Truck Camper from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nomadamerica.com\/booknow-4x4-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nomad America<\/a> that we nicknamed &#x2018;The Blue Beast&#x2019; on <a href=\"http:\/\/instagram.com\/saltinourhair\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">our Instagram<\/a> during our road trip. It had a cabin with sleeping space, a fan, lights, and charging points. On the outside, there was a huge water tank to use as a shower or for cooking, and a cool box in the back kept all of our groceries fresh and cold.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-1080x721.jpg\" alt=\"camper camping in costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"camper camping in costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-78885 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144018\/camping-costa-rica-18-150x100.jpg 150w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/up