io\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Manuel Antonio<\/a>&#xA0;<\/li><li>Camp at <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/kAqebqCABUT78ReL7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Matapalo Beach<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/uvita\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Uvita<\/a> (Camp at <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/AEqCQS4LuNSdxDNK9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">El Tecal<\/a>)<\/li><li>Uvita<\/li><li>Corcovado (Camp at <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/886JSMnzbajgBKpPA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Camping Adonis<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/S8QwUKdU4Q6v3F51A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">at this beach<\/a>)<\/li><li>Corcovado National Park<\/li><li>Corcovado National Park<\/li><li>Towards Puerto Viejo with a night in Orosi<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/puerto-viejo\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Puerto Viejo<\/a> (Camp at <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/ctzXVTrkywp4imyd6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Playa Cocles<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/v1QHTma82t4mx14D9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Camping Arrecife<\/a>)<\/li><li>Puerto Viejo<\/li><li>Puerto Viejo<\/li><li>San Jose (Departure)&#xA0;<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>The incredible team at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nomadamerica.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nomad America<\/a> will also help you out by giving advice when planning your camping road trip with them.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143716\/camping-costa-rica-4.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-imag